sentences.english: It doesn’t matter who you are either. Jaydee always has a way of relating to you.
sentences.chinese: 不仅如此，不管你是谁，杰迪总有方法与你交往。

sentences.english: Not just that, it’s transformed the relationship with myself.
sentences.chinese: 不仅如此，也改善我自己与他人的关系。

sentences.english: But there is more to it than this. Marriage itself is a wealth-generating institution.
sentences.chinese: 不仅如此，婚姻本身就是一种产生财富的机制。

sentences.english: Moreover, his book had great historiography value yet.
sentences.chinese: 不仅如此，《说文引经考》还具有重要的史学价值。

sentences.english: Not only this, you also get the advantage of knowing whether the water is cold or hot.
sentences.chinese: 不仅如此，你还可以通过这款水龙头知道水的冷热。

sentences.english: Not only that, she is unable to walk and in a wheelchair.
sentences.chinese: 不仅如此，她还无法行走，只能坐轮椅。

sentences.english: Not only that, I realized that there is more for me when I saw the following hadith .
sentences.chinese: 不仅如此，当我看到以下圣训时，发现它的意义更大。

sentences.english: What's more, Hanzhong is full of green and vitalities.
sentences.chinese: 不仅如此，汉中更是充满的绿色，充满了活力。

sentences.english: You’ll also save lots of money in storage and maintenance.
sentences.chinese: 不仅如此，你还在储藏和维修上省了一笔不少的钱。

sentences.english: Not only that, but we are doing our heads in.
sentences.chinese: 不仅如此，我们还拖垮了我们的脑袋。

sentences.english: Close your eyes and you'll see more than that.
sentences.chinese: 合上秋水你会看到不仅如此。

sentences.english: Not only that, the infrastructure is extremely well managed.
sentences.chinese: 不仅如此，基础设施的管理都相当地出色。

sentences.english: Also, you run the risk of becoming an addict.
sentences.chinese: 不仅如此，你还会冒着成为瘾君子的危险。

sentences.english: More than that, we create games around the law of gravity.
sentences.chinese: 不仅如此，我们利用定律发明游戏。

sentences.english: Not only that, but they are also special friends to me.
sentences.chinese: 不仅如此，他们还是我特别亲密的朋友。

sentences.english: Not only that, but your parents.
sentences.chinese: 不仅如此，还要孝敬父母。

definition: not only (this one)/not just (...) but also
apart from this/in addition to this
still/still in progress/still more/yet/even more/in addition/fairly/passably (good)/as early as/even/also/else
also/too/(in Classical Chinese) final particle implying affirmation
of/~'s (possessive particle)/(used after an attribute)/(used to form a nominal expression)/(used at the end of a declarative sentence for emphasis)
apart from/other than/except for/external/outside of/on the other side of/beyond
